Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 这里是它的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鬼蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:34.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:40.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于邀请津轻藩的剑术教头月岛源十郎作为虫奉行所的同心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人似乎已经无法行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之前来的 是其公子月岛仁兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:51.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿他对江户安泰能有所贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:59.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【对手是女忍者 火钵】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无…无涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:18.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会成为战无不胜至死方休的强大武士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个糟糕的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:39.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷 今天也请多多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛仁兵卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人 要努力工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:05.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 清晨的修炼 挥刀练习3000遍 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今日起 终于要开始在虫奉行所的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 请您看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:16.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我月岛仁兵卫一定会出色地履行职务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:21.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不辜负江户人们和虫奉行所的同伴们的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 无涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回报您的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:33.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更为了能不断向您靠近 在下一定会变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一大早就这么倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到早会的时间了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~不好意思 您在换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在下就先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次来的新人 一大早就精神充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很快就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:27.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫君 你的伤势如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖您的福 已经痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 无涯大人 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无 无…无涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然全员都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:57.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  首先向仁兵卫君说明一下这里的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过昨日那一战 我想你已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:09.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这日本盘踞着可以吞食人类的巨虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从迄今100年前起便开始肆意横行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:19.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于它们从何而来 又是为何出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今仍在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 在下以前遇到的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过仁兵卫君的故乡津轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及奥州那一带或许是由于气候寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本不应有虫栖息才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:44.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而于10年前 为保护江户民众免受巨虫袭击而设立的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这所新中町奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又称虫奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在虫奉行大人手下 每日从事驱除虫子的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:58.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位虫奉行大人现在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让在下与他见上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫奉行大人从不在人前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人是不可能见得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就连我们也从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 仁兵卫君 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:23.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上 承担着守护江户太平的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:31.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙如此信任 身为武士者已了无遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:39.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我月岛仁兵卫  定会出色完成朝廷所赐的这一职务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨 在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为保护江户之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下定不负各位的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大事不好 松之原大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是从立川往西去了 具体行踪还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家分头搜查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:15.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 仁兵卫君 你暂时在一旁看着学习就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 为何不让在下参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也是虫奉行所的一员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:35.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗 显然是因为你很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:41.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪打正着让你打倒了一只蜘蛛 可能有些沾沾自喜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:45.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里  可没有一个人对小哥你抱有期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家可归的话还是回家比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连 连无涯大人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:02.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一年里进入虫奉行所的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到十天就全部在工作中死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:12.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经没有继续物色人才的精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:18.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此仁兵卫君在这一个月之内禁止拔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是身为与力的我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨…谨遵命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:33.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么偏偏要跟你分到一组啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:45.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下在想无涯大人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对在下来说 无涯大人就是夜空中闪耀的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他深深吸引了在下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也崇拜着无涯大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也 是什么意思 火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:09.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 火钵小姐也跟我一样崇拜着无涯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可比你崇拜他的多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:19.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人到底是怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:31.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人呢 总之就是无人能及的使剑高手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  除此之外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有传言说他在来虫奉行所之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个叫「虫狩」的组织里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虫狩」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个强者云集的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是接受委托 驱除虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实际上谁也说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说到底 传言始终是传言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种神秘之处也是无涯大人的魅力所在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 真不愧是在下所崇拜的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了 是我更崇拜他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 无涯大人是真的很强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 他都曾救过在下的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被救过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵小姐也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:25.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了 请务必将当时的事讲给在下听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你想听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年前离开老家的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的故乡是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于伊贺和甲贺交界处的忍者隐居之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 既不是伊贺流也不是甲贺流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:55.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 在使用炸药进行爆破方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾是首屈一指的忍术一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:05.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到了太平盛世 就不再需要忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:09.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小的时候 人们已经从事着普通的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有曾是一族头领的爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在深山里继续修行着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷子你也是时候该回村子里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么修炼也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今这世道 忍术还有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:42.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵 又到爷爷这儿来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  对孙女倒是疼爱的很
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有在这点上 还算是个普通老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷你看 饭团炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好啊 小火钵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢爷爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是他那只有我能见到的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是穷其一生追求巅峰的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时 我也开始想要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 几年之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:44.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟大人听闻村里有个年轻的女忍者 特地远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要接受在虫奉行所里的职务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能在虫奉行所里崭露头角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷的流派或许就能再次名扬世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:09.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的流派是属于男子的东西 只属于男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽教你 却没有让你继承它的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:22.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我还是想守护爷爷穷其一生心血的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:28.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就决定到虫奉行所任职
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后终于到了我初次执行任务的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他面前 虫子根本不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我便知道了在江户 有真正的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:08.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有一天 自己能强大到足以获得无涯大人的认可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以报答他的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的实力能增进到那种程度 一定能..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 火钵小姐也和在下一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下在蒙无涯大人相救之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切实体会到了父亲所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了父亲所说的 为了不让身后的人为恐惧所吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:35.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人之强 足以驱散身后守护之人的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:44.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一刻 在下就决定了要以无涯大人为前进的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人就是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人想要变成他那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:53.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和你一起说无涯大人说得那么兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 这里是它的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鬼蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是蜻蜓的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鬼蜻蜓一样 对于河畔附近的领地具有强烈的占有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:54.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至日落黄昏 气温下降之时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会为了猎食而开始在空中飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不愧是火钵小姐 知道得真详细
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:07.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 因为这家伙跟我在初次执行任务时遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同一种虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛 你把那两人带到远处去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 火钵小姐 您一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被命令不许拔剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定要一个人消灭这只虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 您一定要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 青鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次执行任务的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能站在无涯大人的身后发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在已经不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫阳花玉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是那时的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止它 凭己之力消灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来证明我的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无…无涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧 火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经照您吩咐 将那两人带到安全之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的猎物 我自己来消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要由我一个人来消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能证明我变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人也一定会认同我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:47.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个职位并不是让您用来证明自己强大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无涯大人也一定是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵小姐您也是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:19:01.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你我 都是被无涯大人那一心只为战而战的身影所吸引的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还轮不到你来说我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把这家伙收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常住战阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝技  小太刀千花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火钵小姐 水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够热
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:21.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫君 你拔剑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:26.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 月岛没有拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:30.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有从剑鞘里拔出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 火钵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今天火药爆破的招数也非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么流派的招数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会告诉别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍宝流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍 珍宝流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声 声音太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:12.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个 死色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系变好些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑术的秘诀在于蒟蒻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:02.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒟蒻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:04.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 现在就开始特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:08.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 请将你那两个「蒟蒻」球借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:09.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵卫大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 虫奉行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:14.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九十九人斩 恋川春菊
