Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,op
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.92,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人忧伤的纯粹简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.97,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕阳西下时的道场一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挥洒着汗水练习刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.98,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.64,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人发笑的满腔热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.02,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有梦想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般这样大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.34,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:49.18,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝阳东升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.25,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你会在喧闹的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拼命奔跑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.27,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.16,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.35,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你会穿过宽阔的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.22,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河滩边诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:09.34,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是这样吧 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:16.61,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.37,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一颗赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:22.53,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守护着重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.46,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}脸上透露着决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつの日か　今よりも　強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ一つの願い　胸に咲く炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もできなかった日に　胸の誓いは生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決してもう逃げださないと　ただひたすら前を向くと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷つき倒れ　また立ち上がる　諦めなど知らぬものに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春は何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先に何がある　見えなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一途なまなざしが　炎を灯すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:38.57,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}希望有一天 能变得比现在更强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:51.41,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}唯一的愿望  如心中绽放的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:10.79,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在一事无成的日子里  心中曾许下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:21.43,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}只会勇往直前 绝不会再逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:30.88,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}受伤倒下  又再站起  在不轻言放弃的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.56,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}春天总会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:44.73,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}前方会有什么  无法预见也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:57.55,mushibugyo_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}坚定的目光  会点燃指引方向的火焰
